---
title: Herby Marinated Chicken & Mayo with Veggie-Packed Cauliflower & Broccoli Rice
description: Say hello to fresh and flavourful! Our pre-marinated chicken thigh is the answer to all your weeknight dinner needs, perfectly paired with a wholesome cauliflower-broccoli rice mix. Add a dollop of creamy mayo on top and you’ve got a tasty, feel-good plate that’s anything but boring.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
